jdrasil.graph

Class GraphWriter

  • java.lang.Object
    • jdrasil.graph.GraphWriter

  • public class GraphWriter
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides various methods to print graphs and tree decomposition to different streams.

        public static <T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>> java.lang.String graphToString(Graph<T> graph)

      • graphToValidString

        public static <T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>> java.lang.String graphToValidString(Graph<T> graph)
        Represents the graph as string the the .gr file format of PACE. In order to do so, a bijection from V to {1,...,|V|} will be computed and vertices will be represented as integers in the output.
        Parameters:
        graph - that should be serialized
        Returns:
        string representing the graph

      • graphToTikZ

        public static <T extends java.lang.Comparable<T>> java.lang.String graphToTikZ(Graph<T> graph)
